702829f.title: Brooklyn: 71st Street - Narrows Avenue
702829f.text:
71st Street, north side, west from Narrows Ave. In the background, may
be seen Shore Road and the Narrows.
May 10, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

702827f-a.title: Brooklyn: 71st Street - Narrows Avenue
702827f-a.text:
33235 71st Street, north side, between Narrows Ave., and Shore
Road, Houses concerned are frame.
May 10, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
